../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/planner.md:28:Central premise: the decisive NS-specific structure may live in trajectory-level deformation and cumulative stretching rather than in Eulerian local estimates. A live route would use one material observable to reach a continuation criterion or a high-vorticity contradiction line.
../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/planner.md:34:Central premise: viscosity changes Kelvin/Cauchy transport into stochastic transport rather than deleting it. If that adapted stochastic backbone is destroyed by Tao-style averaging, it may yield an NS-specific continuation or concentration-exclusion mechanism unavailable to deterministic harmonic-analysis methods.
