../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/attacks/chain-02.md:58:The "positive margin after restoration" language is also too vague. Margin in what norm? Over what continuation threshold? Against which known estimate? Without a quantitative benchmark, this step can devolve into impressionistic judgment.
