+  chosen burden beyond expectation-only rewriting;
+- and the archive still allows the decisive leverage question to stay at
+  representation level instead of estimate level.
+
+So the correct filing is `menu-level setup obstruction`, not a passed Step-1
+entry into exact-identity expansion.
+
+Filed from:
